xbrli:xbrl.in-capmkt:DetailsOfMechanismAvailableToR:
Yes, we have implemented a robust grievance redressal mechanism through the intranet-based HR application “HR
Konnect”, ensuring accessibility for all employees and workers. This system facilitates the prompt, fair, and confidential
handling of grievances across employee categories.
For complaints related to sexual harassment, we adhere strictly to our Prevention of Sexual Harassment (PoSH) Policy,
reinforcing our commitment to a safe and respectful workplace.
In matters involving industrial disputes, we comply with the provisions of the Industrial Disputes Act, 1947 ensuring
legal and effective resolution.
The grievance mechanism includes:
} Clear procedures for raising concerns
} Timely acknowledgment and resolution
} Impartial investigation by designated grievance officers
} Confidentiality and protection against retaliation
} Preventive follow-up measures

